{"tid":1653030,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"環時批評Ted Cruz應被列入禁止訪港黑名單","createTime":"2019-10-14T02:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T03:42:53.000Z","uid":152476,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b2f1c7db9463474b4ac16b11b8a2493e6f94c591","tid":1653030,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:08:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】《環球時報》批評美國共和黨參議員克魯茲亂港，應受到制裁。<br />\n<br />\n社評指，克魯茲特意一身黑衣打扮，是標榜自己與香港抗議者站在一起，嘴上說「非暴力」，只是對挺香港暴力示威的掩護，來港是要阻止理性在這座城市回升，煽動局勢增加熱度，是昨日香港局勢中最突出的破壞性因素之一，讓氣焰已經衰減的示威者產生一縷新幻覺。<br />\n<br />\n社評又指，克魯茲跟激進示威者絕對是一伙，亦想以此在美國撈取政治資本，讓自己更像個旗手性反華政客。如果美國通過所謂《香港人權與民主法案》，克魯茲這類人亦應被列入禁止訪港黑名單，並受到更多制裁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=366144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D366144&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAt5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=afcb8aa1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D366144&h=6d213697\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=366144</a>"},{"pid":"830a259bf2c1e803ea6eab1c44c0050b62cb2929","tid":1653030,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:09:10.000Z","msg":"試下"},{"pid":"efa3f23288c9b27e4e21b8849e45997ba0500a81","tid":1653030,"uid":161125,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:09:32.000Z","msg":"試下囉"},{"pid":"339a2ed163f4b407ed20197a2cb414681343ff61","tid":1653030,"uid":48315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:09:37.000Z","msg":"來吧 美帝等左好耐啦"},{"pid":"c4b74ffb6239b549d150897df9ac016b1aa9436f","tid":1653030,"uid":129142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTi